{"tid":1230647,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"發夢聽到  TVB新聞高層正仆街","createTime":"2019-06-16T09:08:47.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-16T15:11:18.000Z","uid":74332,"like":52,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"ee497b1a8bf4ee14638faffc6bcf86b28e5138bb","tid":1230647,"uid":74332,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-16T09:08:47.000Z","msg":"發夢聽到 上次七警報導出到街 係因為冇比到高層審稿<br />\n今次新聞部大佬24小時坐喺度審稿<br />\n所以烈士犧牲呢單新聞 唔會出到街<br />\n幫我睇下有冇方法傳到呢單嘢出去<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ead3e42b2aae9bd351c96b10904c6aad0a0c7e47","tid":1230647,"uid":236657,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-16T09:09:45.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"8e03f535559126d2d7cc44c88eaa444a95c47969","tid":1230647,"uid":74332,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-16T09:10:27.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e596e677b7dfe98c98d88f1704b227bbb3d14409","tid":1230647,"uid":2896,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-16T09:10:29.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"5d49764eea8e995786ccd89afe4f3bb4ef8eba72","tid":1230647,"uid":74332,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-16T09:10:43.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7b7f1eca26f8acf1c9a409becc2706c05824a829","tid":1230647,"uid":74448,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-16T09:10:54.000Z","msg":"叫花柳哥收皮"},{"pid":"57b89e56bb9693850f0dde2e1283fd85f6baab4f","tid":1230647,"uid":212182,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-16T09:11:38.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"21b968c7f12f0bf09216d0d33f5b5288a69fa60f","tid":1230647,"uid":48295,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-16T09:12:34.000Z","msg":"睇下捱到幾耐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 記得唔好放假"},{"pid":"e3afd53d5e33b06cd17fc7b9b5fc4399785b7fa2","tid":1230647,"uid":74332,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-16T09:15:07.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8ac7e6d0f844f07b38917511a2039586b7b29b6b","tid":1230647,"uid":28252,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-16T09:21:56.000Z","msg":"長輩圖"},{"pid":"4b8be04741a611e481f6c19681840820e13e3186","tid":1230647,"uid":160964,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-16T09:29:14.000Z","msg":"係時候全港罷睇TVB"},{"pid":"2971fad603f289d3f5737f7265ceecda39552c7c","tid":1230647,"uid":107368,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-16T15:11:18.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><strong><br />\n<br />\n繼續做野 <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n</strong></span></span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: medium;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>TVB在反送中報導一事，已經嚴重違反電視通用業務守則中有關「第9章準確、持平及公正」，當中要求「持牌人必須盡一切合理努力，確保新聞、時事節目...的真實資料準確無誤」，以及「持牌人必須確保新聞節目...能夠恰當地持平」，「不可使用謬誤資料或歪曲事實。持牌人亦不應錯誤引導觀眾，以致對節目提及的人士或團體不公平」<br />\n<br />\nTVB在反送中的報導完全扭曲事相，報導嚴重偏袒警方和政府，報導失實 ， 偏頗，例如6月12日的「六點半新聞報道」和「晚間新聞」，完全不播放及不提及：<br />\n1. 警方違法向多名記者開槍，棍打記者<br />\n2. 警方違法瞄準市民頭部發射布袋彈和橡膠子彈<br />\n3. 在沒有任何襲擊下，警方違法向婦孺、伯伯開槍<br />\n4. 警方違法向市民投擲鐵枝、磗頭<br />\n5. 隻字不提一些市民向警方掟水樽垃圾等之前，警方在多處在沒有受到任何襲擊，提出任何警告下，違法突然向市民開槍，不斷發射催淚彈，布袋彈和橡膠子彈，導致局勢快速失控<br />\n6.隻字不提有市民於6月15日於太古廣場因展示示威標語墮樓, 送院搶救後不治的事實<br />\n<br />\n投訴表格：<a href=\"https://apps.coms-auth.hk/apps/broadcasting_complaint/index.aspx?lang=2\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fapps.coms-auth.hk%2Fapps%2Fbroadcasting_complaint%2Findex.aspx%3Flang%3D2&d=p84ZIGfbRlzA5dgw%2Bb26WC6Ol0HYJA13lVA%2BPgi6hPY%3D&h=230ed666\" target=\"_blank\">https://apps.coms-auth.hk/apps/broadcasting_complaint/index.aspx?lang=2</a></strong></span></span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n